data.description: Cutest home in the neighborhood? This property in the cozy community of Circle Pines has it all. Walk into the beautifully updated kitchen to see stainless steel appliances, luxury vinyl plank flooring and sparkling white cabinets. In the dining room there is a charming side bar with a wine fridge on your way to the private deck to enjoy entertainment with friends & family. Backyard is a private oasis, completely fenced in with storage shed, multi-zone irrigation system and wonderful landscaping. Close proximity to parks, dining, entertainment, freeway access and in the coveted Centennial School District. Welcome home.
